author: Google
description:
Have you tried Gemini 3 Pro yet? Discover what’s new with Gemini by trying these three prompts.

- Plan a 3-day trip to Rome: Uses Visual Layout to provide an immersive, visual itinerary for you to explore, powered by Gemini 3's multimodal capabilities.

- Ask Gemini about the Van Gogh gallery: Uses Dynamic View and advanced agentic coding capabilities to create an interactive interface where you can tap, scroll, and learn.

- Organize your inbox: The Gemini Agent can help with tedious, multi-step tasks on your behalf while keeping you in control.

#GoogleGemini #Gemini3
title: Gemini 3 is now in the Gemini app. See what's new with these 3 prompts

author: Google
description:
Missed our Gemini 3 vibe coding  livestream? We’ve condensed the chaos and creativity into one essential recap. 

Watch the team and special guests put Gemini 3 to the test live—building games in one shot, vibe coding in AI Studio, and revealing our next-gen agentic platform. See how the model handles complex reasoning and real-time app generation without breaking a sweat. Here’s what they covered:

- One-Shot Games: Watch Gemini 3 build a working Flight Simulator (complete with a "Sponsored by Google" blimp) and a Fishing Game set in an Oklahoma sunset.
- Vibe Coding: See how developers are using AI Studio to go from a simple prompt to a deployed app in minutes.
- Creative Tools: Using the model to visualize 3D dance formations from a simple video input.
- Antigravity Reveal: Our first look at "Antigravity," the next-generation agentic development platform for professional builders.
- Model Performance: Why the jump from 2.5 Pro to Gemini 3 changes the game for accuracy and "one-shot
title: Recap: Vibe Coding with Gemini 3 on Launch Day
